<LI>What if we&nbsp;had a minimum level cap of say level 2-10 for bazaar entrance, it might cut down on the plat sellers?&nbsp; If the plat sellers don't know how to play the game maybe it would be that much more of a discouragement?&nbsp; I mean honestly anything to help get rid of them I am sure none of us would&nbsp;complain about it would we?</LI></UL>
<DIV>[snip]</DIV><BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<DIV>The same people who sell platinum also pay poor wages for people to level characters and then sell the accounts (there was a post about this but I can't find it... I know Chantenya was involved in the discussion). Go look at some of the auction sites, it is interesting to see how blatent they are in promoting their goods. You can look up magelo profiles for their 'for sale' accounts and let me assure you that they are not selling level 10 characters.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Frankly, SOE could be doing a lot to prevent this stuff, but they aren't. I suspect that if SOE changes the game to make it harder for RL cash exchanges, the RL cash exchanges will come up with new ways to do their business. This would turn into an arms race that would only hurt the regular gamer who plays by the rules.</DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1069548" target=new resize="true"><img src="http://i22.photobucket.com/albums/b319/vaedian/vaedian_75x75_named.jpg"></a> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1153949" target=new resize="true"><img src="http://i22.photobucket.com/albums/b319/vaedian/lixea_75x75_named.jpg"></a> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1236981" target=new resize="true"><img src="http://i22.photobucket.com/albums/b319/vaedian/davven_75x75_named.jpg"></a> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1264108" target=new resize="true"><img src="http://i22.photobucket.com/albums/b319/vaedian/tisha_75x75_named.jpg"></a><br>What the **HALFLING**? Because smurfs just aren't RP.
